02:38.533 --> 02:40.618
{\an1}DID YOU EAT
ANOTHER SOLICITOR?

02:40.702 --> 02:41.786
MM-MM.

02:41.870 --> 02:43.454
{\an1}WELL, I'LL
SEE ABOUT THAT.

02:43.538 --> 02:44.455
(<i> clanging</i> )

02:44.539 --> 02:46.541
(<i> offscreen laughing</i> )

02:46.624 --> 02:47.709
