06:15.083 --> 06:18.336
GO TO HOLLOWOOD, FIND HIM.

06:18.419 --> 06:19.462
HERE'S THREE BUCKS.

06:19.545 --> 06:21.547
BRING HIM HOME TO US,
WON'T YOU?

06:21.631 --> 06:23.424
Mr. Bighead:
BEV.

06:23.508 --> 06:27.011
