KEEP YOUR SKIN ON, FROGMAN.

06:27.095 --> 06:28.137
OH, ROCKO

06:28.221 --> 06:32.642
{\an1}I CAN'T BELIEVE WE'RE
REALLY GOING TO HOLLOWOOD.

06:32.725 --> 06:33.935
I'M SO EXCITED.

06:34.018 --> 06:35.394
ME NEITHER, FILBURT.

06:35.478 --> 06:38.272
{\an1}I JUST HOPE SPUNKY'S
GOING TO BE OKAY.

06:38.356 --> 06:38.856
I LEFT FOOD FOR HIM.

06:38.940 --> 06:42.026
(<i> burping</i> )

06:42.693 --> 06:46.656
(<i> blowing raspberries</i> )

06:46.739 --> 06:48.866
(<i> tires squealing</i> )

06:53.412 --> 06:54.789
Filbert:
WOW...

06:54.872 --> 06:57.667
IT'S SO REAL.

06:59.001 --> 07:01.170
Rocko:
THIS LOOKS LIKE IT, FILBURT.

07:02.296 --> 07:03.756
(<i> buzzing</i> )

07:03.840 --> 07:07.051
{\an5}(<i> falsetto:</i> )
HI, THERE, WELCOME
