07:10.138 --> 07:11.848
OH, HELLO.

07:11.931 --> 07:14.058
I'M SORRY, WE'VE
JUST COME ALONG

07:14.142 --> 07:18.104
TO SEE IF WE MIGHT MEET WITH
RALPH BIGHEAD THIS AFTERNOON.

07:18.187 --> 07:21.482
THE... TOUR'S
VERY NICE, YOU KNOW.

07:21.566 --> 07:22.692
WELL, I'M...

07:22.775 --> 07:24.986
YES, UM, I'M SURE IT IS.

07:26.904 --> 07:28.990
(<i> lower voice:</i> )
LET'S TRY THIS AGAIN.

07:29.073 --> 07:30.032
(<i> clearing throat</i> )

07:30.116 --> 07:32.827
{\an1}(<i> falsetto</i> ):
WELCOME TO BIGHEAD STUDIOS.

07:32.910 --> 07:36.664
{\an1}HAVE YOU FOLKS COME FOR OUR
EXCITING NEW STUDIO TOUR?

07:36.747 --> 07:39.292
UM, WELL, I...

07:39.375 --> 07:43.212
{\an1}YES, YES, UM, WE'D LOVE
TO TAKE YOUR TOUR.

07:47.133 --> 07:48.718
ALL ABOARD.

07:48.801 --> 07:49.719
HELLO, EVERYONE.

07:49.802 --> 07:51.971
WELCOME TO RALPH
BIGHEAD STUDIOS

07:52.054 --> 07:53.556
HOME OF THE FATHEADS

07:53.639 --> 07:56.809
AMERICA'S GOOFIEST
CARTOON COUPLE.

