OKAY, SO WE GOT MR.
AND MRS. FATHEAD.

08:20.958 --> 08:22.251
AH, HERE WE GO.

08:22.335 --> 08:24.587
AND THEY'RE, YOU KNOW,
STANDING THERE.

08:24.670 --> 08:28.591
IN THE NEXT PANEL,
THE PHONE RINGS AND MRS. FATHEAD

08:28.674 --> 08:31.552
{\an1}REACHES OFFSCREEN
AND ANSWERS THE PHONE

08:31.636 --> 08:32.761
AND SAYS, "HELLO?"

08:32.845 --> 08:33.804
HUH? HUH?

08:33.888 --> 08:36.849
OH, GENIUS.

08:38.351 --> 08:41.229
{\an5}Rhino:
NEXT WE VISIT
THE ANIMATION DEPARTMENT

08:41.312 --> 08:44.148
{\an1}WHERE OUR ANIMATORS
BRING THE STORY TO LIFE.

08:44.232 --> 08:47.610
{\an1}HERE WE FIND A GROUP
OF ANIMATORS HARD AT WORK

08:47.693 --> 08:50.821
{\an1}DRAWING THOUSANDS
OF TEENY TINY PICTURES

08:50.905 --> 08:52.949
AGAIN AND AGAIN AND AGAIN.

08:53.032 --> 08:56.118
(<i> phone ringing</i> )

08:56.202 --> 08:57.536
HEY, FILBURT

08:57.620 --> 08:58.955
DON'T TAP ON THE GLASS.

08:59.038 --> 09:03.125
OH, OKAY, ROCKO.

09:05.002 --> 09:06.295
Filbert:
OH, BOY.

09:06.379 --> 09:08.756
Rhino:
NEXT STOP, THE CAMERA ROOM

09:08.839 --> 09:13.511
{\an1}WHERE THE FINISHED ANIMATION
IS METICULOUSLY FILMED.

09:13.594 --> 09:14.929
GO, HONEY, GO.

09:15.012 --> 09:16.097
OH, THAT'S FANTASTIC.

09:16.180 --> 09:18.891
YES, SPARKLE, BABY.

09:18.975 --> 09:21.644
