09:47.962 --> 09:50.089
NOPE, NOT ANY PART OF IT.

09:50.172 --> 09:52.800
HELLO, HELLO, HELLO!

09:54.093 --> 09:57.596
(<i> laughing</i> )

09:57.680 --> 09:58.764
WHERE'S THE PAIN?

