THE ANIMATION INDUSTRY

10:15.156 --> 10:18.075
{\an1}THE LIFEBLOOD OF
ITS VERY EXISTENCE

10:19.827 --> 10:20.870
Filbert:
T-T-T...

10:20.953 --> 10:21.829
TOYS.

10:23.956 --> 10:26.375
OOH...

10:26.459 --> 10:28.461
OH, OH, I WANT
ONE OF THESE

10:28.544 --> 10:31.213
AND ONE OF THESE,
AND, AND, OH...

10:31.297 --> 10:33.507
TWO OF THESE,
AND TWO OF THOSE

10:33.591 --> 10:35.634
AND ONE OF THOSE
AND TWO OF THOSE

10:35.718 --> 10:37.219
AND ONE OF THESE
AND THOSE AND THESE

10:37.303 --> 10:38.512
AND 12 OF THOSE.

