10:41.265 --> 10:44.352
OH, OH, OH, OH, OH.

10:44.435 --> 10:47.063
LOOK, LOOK, LOOK, LOOK.

10:47.146 --> 10:49.732
{\an1}(<i> gulping</i> ):
