10:56.822 --> 10:58.949
YES, YES, YES, YES...

10:59.033 --> 11:03.329
{\an5}Crowd:
YES, SIR. YES, SIR.
YOU'VE GOT IT, R.B..

11:04.330 --> 11:05.873
R.B.?

11:05.956 --> 11:07.666
R.B.!

11:07.750 --> 11:09.251
FILBURT, FILBURT.

11:09.335 --> 11:11.170
THAT WAS RALPH BIGHEAD.

11:11.253 --> 11:13.047
WHAT? WHO? WHEN? WHERE?

11:13.130 --> 11:15.257
OKAY, GUYS.

11:15.341 --> 11:19.178
