11:20.930 --> 11:22.056
GUYS?

11:22.139 --> 11:24.266
YOO-HOO!

11:24.350 --> 11:27.269
{\an4}All:
YES, YES,
YES, ABSOLUTELY.

11:27.353 --> 11:29.438
{\an1}YES, YES, CERTAINLY,
WON'T WE?

11:29.522 --> 11:31.357
(<i> phone ringing</i> )

11:31.440 --> 11:33.275
{\an1}CERTAINLY,
RIGHT AWAY, YES.

11:34.860 --> 11:36.862
Ralph:
YOU'RE ALL FIRED.

11:37.988 --> 11:40.574
(<i> all chatting</i> )

11:43.369 --> 11:45.579
I THOUGHT I FIRED YOU.

11:45.663 --> 11:48.582
UH, WELL, WE DON'T
WORK FOR YOU.

11:51.127 --> 11:52.086
HEH-HEH.

11:52.169 --> 11:53.754
HEH-HEH-HEH.

11:53.838 --> 11:58.217
{\an1}WELL, THEN, WHY
ARE YOU IN MY OFFICE?

11:58.300 --> 12:01.178
WE LOVE YOUR CARTOON.

12:02.263 --> 12:04.432
BUT ACTUALLY, THAT'S
NOT WHY WE'RE HERE.

12:04.515 --> 12:06.225
WE'RE HERE
ABOUT YOUR PARENTS.

12:06.308 --> 12:08.436
I HAVE NO PARENTS.

12:08.519 --> 12:11.313
NO, UH, ACTUALLY,
UH, YOU DO.

12:11.397 --> 12:13.649
RIGHT NEXT DOOR
TO MY HOUSE, YOU SEE.

12:13.732 --> 12:16.235
{\an1}AND THEY'RE HAVING
THEIR 30th WEDDING ANNIVERSARY

12:16.318 --> 12:18.279
ON SATURDAY NIGHT.

12:18.362 --> 12:19.780
IN THE VIKING ROOM.

12:19.864 --> 12:22.491
{\an1}YES, YES, IN THE VIKING ROOM
AT THE HOLIDAY HOTEL.

12:22.575 --> 12:25.619
{\an1}AND THEY WANT
YOU TO BE THERE.

12:25.703 --> 12:28.706
{\an1}YOU SEE, THEY MISS
YOU AND, AND, AND...

12:28.789 --> 12:30.875
AND THEY LOVE YOUR CARTOON.

12:30.958 --> 12:32.835
{\an1}IT WOULD MEAN A LOT
TO THEM

12:32.918 --> 12:34.837
IF YOU
COULD BE THERE.

12:34.920 --> 12:37.506
