{\an1}HONEY, DO YOU
HEAR SOMETHING?

13:47.117 --> 13:48.494
WAIT A MINUTE.

13:48.577 --> 13:52.039
{\an1}NOW, THAT TIME,
I DEFINITELY HEARD SOMETHING.

